workout_groups.name: Jo Staff Techniques Training
workout_groups.description: Specific techniques for Jo staff training.

workouts.name: Tsuki (Thrust)
workouts.description: Practice the Tsuki thrust technique for 5 minutes.

workouts.name: Uchi (Strike)
workouts.description: Practice the Uchi strike technique for 5 minutes.

workouts.name: Hiki Otoshi (Dropping Strike)
workouts.description: Practice the Hiki Otoshi dropping strike technique for 10 minutes.

workouts.name: Kaeshi Waza (Counter Techniques)
workouts.description: Practice Kaeshi Waza counter techniques for 15 minutes.

workouts.name: Mawari Waza (Spinning Techniques)
workouts.description: Practice Mawari Waza spinning techniques for 20 minutes.

workouts.name: Kuzushi (Breaking Balance)
workouts.description: Practice Kuzushi breaking balance techniques for 10 minutes.

workouts.name: Kuzushi with Sparring
workouts.description: Practice Kuzushi breaking balance techniques with sparring for 15 minutes.

workouts.name: Kuzushi with Sparring and Resistance Bands
workouts.description: Practice Kuzushi breaking balance techniques with sparring and resistance bands for 15 minutes.

workouts.name: Weighted Vest Kuzushi with Sparring
workouts.description: Practice Kuzushi breaking balance techniques with weighted vest and sparring for 15 minutes.

workout_groups.name: Advanced Jo Staff Techniques
workout_groups.description: Advanced techniques for Jo staff training.

workouts.name: Muso Gamae (Ready Stance)
workouts.description: Practice Muso Gamae ready stance technique for 10 minutes.

workouts.name: Kaiten Nage (Rotational Throw)
workouts.description: Practice Kaiten Nage rotational throw technique for 15 minutes.

workouts.name: Sankyo (Third Control)
workouts.description: Practice Sankyo third control technique for 20 minutes.

workouts.name: Irimi Nage (Entering Throw)
workouts.description: Practice Irimi Nage entering throw technique for 20 minutes.

workouts.name: Shiho Nage (Four-Direction Throw)
workouts.description: Practice Shiho Nage four-direction throw technique for 20 minutes.

workouts.name: Kokyu Nage (Breath Throw)
workouts.description: Practice Kokyu Nage breath throw technique for 15 minutes.

workouts.name: Kote Gaeshi (Wrist Twist)
workouts.description: Practice Kote Gaeshi wrist twist technique for 20 minutes.

workouts.name: Tenkan (Pivoting)
workouts.description: Practice Tenkan pivoting technique for 15 minutes.

workouts.name: Ushiro Waza (Rear Techniques)
workouts.description: Practice Ushiro Waza rear techniques for 20 minutes.
